" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00878-TW</a>)</p></section><section><p>4. 外資累計買超 2 日的股票<br/>元大台灣50 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0050-TW</a>)、凱基台灣TOP50 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:009816:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/009816\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">009816-TW</a>)、友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>)、中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)、國泰永續高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00878:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00878-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>5. 外資當日 (10) 買超的股票<br/>元大台灣50 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0050-TW</a>)、凱基台灣TOP50 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:009816:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/009816\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">009816-TW</a>)、國泰永續高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00878:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00878-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
